domeeko lig_prep — docking-ready ligand preparation

USAGE:
  domeeko lig_prep --lig_dir DIR [options]

DESCRIPTION:
  Performs 3D optimization and PDBQT generation.

OPTIONS:
  --lig_dir DIR
  --steps N         MMFF optimization steps (default: 5000)
  --ff NAME         MMFF94 | MMFF94s | UFF | GAFF

EXAMPLES:
  domeeko lig_prep --lig_dir ligands
  domeeko lig_prep --lig_dir ligands --steps 10000 --ff UFF
